{"tid":1139174,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"孩提好友分隔12年重逢 拍拖7年終成眷屬","createTime":"2019-05-05T05:09:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-05T07:07:25.000Z","uid":72009,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b6cbef3c2cead689de26eb4ee1bc24d57aacee37","tid":1139174,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T05:09:40.000Z","msg":"克羅(Natalie Crowe)與塔曼(Austin Tatman)是幼兒學前班同學，當時是班上最好朋友。在1999年，克羅隨家人從佛羅里達州遷往康涅狄格州，兩人因此失去聯絡。直至2012年克羅唸中學時，有天偶爾翻看母親的舊地址簿，腦海首先冒出的，就是塔曼的名字。她說，直至今天，她仍不知為何突然想起塔曼。<br />\n<br />\n克羅透過Facebook聯絡上塔曼，問他是否仍記得她，塔曼表示記得。兩人之後交換電話號碼，並相約見面。由於兩人在不同州份上中學，所以一直維持分隔兩地的關係，直到上大學時，克羅才重返佛州。<br />\n<br />\n塔曼2017年向克羅求婚，兩人上月在佛州舉行婚禮。婚禮的賓客名冊，特意設計成舊地址簿模樣，以紀念這根促成一段千里姻緣的紅線。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190505/large/1557011725_d499.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190505%2Flarge%2F1557011725_d499.jpg&h=50593eb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fa7d52e889341d2deb39e3e45d3d90c65dce463","tid":1139174,"uid":2429,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T05:27:40.000Z","msg":"高等白人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ded048bdbaac7cd0d26a00eb363eceda9774007b","tid":1139174,"uid":77277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T06:20:41.000Z","msg":"好sweet<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d73a727ab0491f0f5cae75488506e44418e3c03c","tid":1139174,"uid":61954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T07:02:33.000Z","msg":"青梅竹馬ending<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b29049940776dd459a1eab9a325acbbb18a0ac45","tid":1139174,"uid":117679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T07:07:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係每對都好似童話⋯⋯"}]}